= cerealize 0.8.0
by Cardinal Blue ( http://cardinalblue.com )

== LINKS:

* github[http://github.com/cardinalblue/cerealize]
* rubygems[http://rubygems.org/gems/cerealize]

== DESCRIPTION:

  Serialize out of the Cerealize Box
  cerealize - a drop-in replacement for ActiveRecord's serialize
  DataMapper support planed.

== SYNOPSIS:

 require 'cerealize'
 class User < ActiveRecord::Base
   cerealize :data, Hash, :encoding => :marshal
 end

== REQUIREMENTS:

* activerecord currently, dm-core support planed.

== INSTALL:

> gem install cerealize
or
> script/plugin install git://github.com/cardinalblue/cerealize.git

